# KEYBOARD SHORTCUTS (PYCHARM)

Run current file:           Shift + F10
Debug current file:         Shift + F9
Toggle breakpoint:          Ctrl + F8
Step into function:         F7
Step over line:            F8
Resume program:            F9
View variable value:       Hover mouse
Open project files:        Ctrl + Alt + Shift + S

